title: Dark Possession by Phaedra Weldon
description:
After losing her power to the Wraith, Rhonda Orly works hard picking up the pieces of her life. She leaves the Society, buys a house, finds a new job, and turns her attention toward her future and away from the Planes that dominated her life. 
But there are forces that seek out Rhonda's knowledge, and her lost power. These forces have other plans for a Child of the Society of Ishmael.
